snippet.title: Post Trauma Official Announcement Trailer | The Game Awards 2022
snippet.description:
We got an eerie look at the psychological horror and retro-style puzzles of the classic style, fixed camera angle game Post Trauma, coming to PC and console. 

#posttrauma #thegameawards #gaming
